Instructions:

Create the directory:

bash
Copy code
mkdir -p alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss
cd alx-intermediate-frontend/0x03-sass_scss
Install Node.js v20.16 via NVM (Linux):

bash
Copy code
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
exit  # close and reopen your terminal
nvm install 20.16
Install Sass version 3.7.4:

bash
Copy code
npm install sass@3.7.4
